      <item>
        <title>Responsive Grid</title>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Presentation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CSS117 is a very smart and flexible grid where you don’t need to wrap individual rows nor to tag last columns with classes. It is highly customizable through &lt;a href=&quot;#customize-variables&quot;&gt;variables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the following example, one row become two rows in the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium&lt;/code&gt; breakpoint:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;doc&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;grid&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;cols&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&gt; large-4 &lt;strong&gt;medium-12&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&gt; large-4 &lt;strong&gt;medium-6&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&gt; large-4 &lt;strong&gt;medium-6&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;installation&quot;&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Download via bower (&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;bower install css117&lt;/code&gt;) or from the Github repo (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/aastudio/CSS117/archive/master.zip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;master.zip&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/code&gt; in your main &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;.scss&lt;/code&gt; file the partials &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;css117-grid.scss&lt;/code&gt; (located in &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;src/layout/&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;From it, copy from its two maps (&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-settings&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-breakpoints&lt;/code&gt;) in your project before the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/code&gt; and remove the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;!default&lt;/code&gt; flag&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;example-&quot;&gt;Example :&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// Variables
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-settings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;grid-class-name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;grid&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;cols-class-name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cols&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col-class-name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;col&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;nb-of-columns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;max-width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;          &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1000px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;gutter-width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;20px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;grid-margin-top&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;grid-margin-bottom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;grid-padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col-margin-top&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col-margin-bottom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col-padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;20px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col-font-size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1rem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;centered&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;full-width-on-small&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;offset-class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;offset-class-name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;offset&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;visibility-class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;                &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;debug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-breakpoints&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;medium&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;800px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;small&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;500px&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// Import
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;bower_components/css117/src/layout/css117-grid&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;set-up-your-html&quot;&gt;Set up your html&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Set up your html as followed :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;grid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;cols&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6 small-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-6 small-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-3 small-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-2 medium-4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-2 medium-4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-2 medium-4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTE :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;The two wrappers, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;.grid&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;.cols&lt;/code&gt;, are mandatory (the secret sauce of the grid)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;The classes &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium-&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small-&lt;/code&gt; are created automatically from the map &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-breakpoints&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;The widest breakpoint is always called &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;large&lt;/code&gt; and the narrowest &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; (both are mandatory)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;You can add any other breakpoint between, directly in the map &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-breakpoints&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;customize-variables&quot;&gt;Customize variables&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Below are the variables from the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$css117-grid-settings&lt;/code&gt; SASS map :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;SASS variables&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;Default&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;Type&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;grid-class-name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;grid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Customize the first wrapper class name&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;cols-class-name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;cols&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Customize the second wrapper class name&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col-class-name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Customize columns class name&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;nb-of-columns&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;12&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;integer&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the number of columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;max-width&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;960px&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the max-width of the grid&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;gutter-width&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the width of gutters&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;grid-margin-top&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;0&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the margin bottom of the grid&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;grid-margin-bottom&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the margin bottom of the grid&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;grid-padding&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;0&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the padding of the grid (can be this way : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;30px 10px 0 5px&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col-margin-top&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;0&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the margin bottom of columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col-margin-bottom&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the margin bottom of columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col-padding&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;20px&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;pixels&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the padding of columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;col-font-size&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;1rem&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;rem&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Define the base font-size inside columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;centered&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Choose &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; to center the grid on the page&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;full-width-on-small&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Choose &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; to have a unique &lt;a href=&quot;#fullwidth-on-small-breakpoints&quot;&gt;fullwidth&lt;/a&gt; on the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; breakpoint&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;offset-class&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Choose &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; if you need &lt;a href=&quot;&quot;&gt;offset classes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;offset-class-name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;offset&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Customize name of offset classes. Works if &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;offset&lt;/code&gt; is set to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;visibility-class&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Choose &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; if you need &lt;a href=&quot;&quot;&gt;visibility classes&lt;/a&gt; that let you show or hide columns based on screen size. It creates a &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;-hidden&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;-visible&lt;/code&gt; classes. For instance : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;large-hidden&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium-visible&lt;/code&gt;, …&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;If set to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;, it adds a pink transparent background-color behind elements and blue sides border to each columns&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;debug&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;boolean&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;If set to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;, it send debugging information to the ‘Terminal’&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;fullwidth-on-small-breakpoints&quot;&gt;Fullwidth on small breakpoints&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By default on the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; breakpoint, each column of has different size, but in actual use, you probably want to set a unique fullwidth.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then you don’t need the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; class on your markup :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;grid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;cols&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;doc&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;grid&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;cols&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&gt;large-4 medium-6&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&gt;large-4 medium-6&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&gt;large-4 medium-12&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;offset-classes&quot;&gt;Offset classes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Offset classes let you indent some columns.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;grid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;cols&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 large-offset-2 medium-no-offset medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-6 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;doc&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;grid&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;cols&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-12&quot;&gt; large-12 &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-4 large-offset-2 medium-no-offset medium-6&quot;&gt; large-4&lt;br /&gt;large-offset-2&lt;br /&gt;medium-no-offset&lt;br /&gt;medium-6 &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-6 medium-6&quot;&gt; large-6 medium-6 &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-12&quot;&gt; large-12 &lt;/div&gt;
            ...
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;It is written &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;BREAKPOINT-offset-NUMBER&lt;/code&gt;. Example : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;large-offset-2&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium-offset-7&lt;/code&gt;, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;It comes also no-offset classes : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium-no-offset&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small-no-offset&lt;/code&gt;, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;visibility-classes&quot;&gt;Visibility classes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Visibility classes let you show or hide columns based on screen size. It creates a -hidden and -visible classes : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;large-hidden&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;medium-visible&lt;/code&gt;, etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;grid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;cols&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-12 medium-hidden&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; ... &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-hidden medium-visible medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-12 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;doc&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;grid&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;cols&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-12 medium-hidden&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#52707E; color:#fff;&quot;&gt; large-12 medium-hidden &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-hidden medium-visible medium-6&quot;&gt; large-hidden medium-visible medium-6 &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;col large-12 medium-6&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#BFDBC6;&quot;&gt; large-12 medium-6 &lt;/div&gt;
            ...
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
